實自己一個更開心"},{"pid":"cd94627faedaa7bd1943421c17016e262fdc35e3","tid":1191082,"uid":152040,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T18:33:10.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好放佢出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d255c7afcca1255415b5ddd146444485e2655af2","tid":1191082,"uid":257651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T18:33:12.000Z","msg":"從客觀嘅角度睇如果佢嘅脾氣係無理取鬧當然係唔合理<br />\n但如果佢嘅脾氣係來自於你做咗一啲佢唔鍾意嘅事而發脾氣，仲可以情有可原。咁你係咪完全都冇發過脾氣先，其實都係互相遷就嘅啫，佢都有機會包容左你一啲野而你唔知，無人完美，老老實實好少女朋友真係唔會無脾氣，唔想受氣嘅你咪唔好拍拖囉，其實自己一個更開心"},{"pid":"7e39828bb85302e751bc8349d74208fe6352600d","tid":1191082,"uid":6988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbc888516793f0bc312c566d5e014cf299239720","tid":1191082,"uid":97851,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3ada8a3ddedcfcb80d336e95e62ffa5495c3a31e","tid":1191082,"uid":81345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"15431cc466541363f88f0df347127611b9edaa56","tid":1191082,"uid":97851,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T17:45:15.000Z","msg":"痴線！！！<br />\n以為係我男朋友開po.....<br />\n其實我都好想知 其實應該點先好<br />\n佢從來唔會哄我 佢係超大男人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T17:52:26.000Z","msg":"咁咪搵過個會哄你囉<br />\n反正你都著眼於佢有庶哄你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T17:56:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T18:55:56.000Z","msg":"屌 絲打同我諗嘅野完全一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5c3bb2b9e315e82e92f7fdd146dd9ffcce15e3","tid":1191082,"uid":97851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e39828bb85302e751bc8349d74208fe6352600d","tid":1191082,"uid":6988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbc888516793f0bc312c566d5e014cf299239720","tid":1191082,"uid":97851,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3ada8a3ddedcfcb80d336e95e62ffa5495c3a31e","tid":1191082,"uid":81345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06